data.description: Welcome to this charming 2-bed, 2-bath home complete with an upper floor home office, creek front location on Elk Creek. The property also features a spacious shop with power, water, and a kitchenette, perfect for your hobbies or projects. Inside, you'll find both a living and family room, a dedicated laundry room, and modern plumbing with galvanized pipes replaced by PEX. Additional amenities include a new water line to the home, full RV hookups with electric and sewer dump, fast fiber optic internet, vinyl plank flooring, and a main bedroom with a walk-in closet. All of this is set in a fantastic yard, making it the perfect place to call home.
